      public TableColumnBuilder<S,T> apply(Consumer<TableColumn<S,T>> func)
      Applies a function to the TableColumn instance currently being built. Most operations on the instance can be performed using this method.

      Example usage:

      
 apply(tableColumn -> tableColumn.setId("Main" + tableColumn.getTypeSelector()))
